snippet.title: Best VGM 1209 - Mega Man X - Spark Mandrill Stage
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 409 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mpt-RXhdZzQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Mega Man X (1993)
Spark Mandrill Stage
Setsuo Yamamoto, Makoto Tomozawa, Yuki Iwai, Yuko Takehara & Toshihiko Horiyama
